    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Psolus steuarti sp. nov. holotype (a – c, NMV F 157398): a, dorsal view; b, lateral view (insert, thick granules); c, ventral view; paratype (d – f, NMV F 157399): d, sole ossicle; e, dorsal ossicles (multi-layered scales, perforated plates and cups); f, tentacle ossicles." ;
